data.description: Beautiful one owner modern day home. Like new. 3 bedroom 2 baths upstairs. Unfinished basement with plenty of potential. House offers tankless water heater as well as gently used furnace and HVAC. Mature landscape in front and back yard. Vivint security system equipment installed and to be paid off at closing. Listing will be entered with agent in MLS after the 26th. Contact listing agent in regards to solar.
